name: Technelegy: “Your imagination is not what you told it to be.”
description: A line of transhuman poetry written in 2019 by GPT-2, in collaboration with @sashastiles. Minted 2021 in an edition of 20. Part of the ongoing @technelegy project, probing what it means to be human in a nearly post-human era. www.sashastiles.com #technelegy #arspoeticacybernetica
